00:01:54.450 --> 00:01:56.710
So we are now in this situation.

00:01:56.710 --> 00:01:59.700
This is the new price.

00:01:59.700 --> 00:02:03.250
Now, they say what is the new
level of domestic production?

00:02:03.250 --> 00:02:05.560
So the domestic supply, at that price,

00:02:05.560 --> 00:02:09.300
the domestic suppliers look
like they are willing to

00:02:09.300 --> 00:02:12.140
supply six million pounds.

00:02:12.140 --> 00:02:15.440
So that is our new level
of domestic production,

00:02:15.440 --> 00:02:18.470
six million pounds.

00:02:18.470 --> 00:02:20.460
All right, part ii,

00:02:20.460 --> 00:02:24.540
calculate the domestic
consumer surplus for Loriland.

