00:03:28.290 --> 00:03:29.810
10 million

00:03:29.810 --> 00:03:32.060
pounds times,

00:03:32.060 --> 00:03:36.087
we have a difference of $5 per pound,

00:03:36.087 --> 00:03:36.990
$5

00:03:37.900 --> 00:03:39.520
per pound.

00:03:39.520 --> 00:03:42.290
And then, of course, we want
to multiply it times 1/2,

00:03:42.290 --> 00:03:43.950
so this one right over here.

00:03:43.950 --> 00:03:46.690
So let's see, the pounds cancel out.

00:03:46.690 --> 00:03:48.780
And so, if you multiply it out,

00:03:48.780 --> 00:03:52.080
this is going to be $50 million times 1/2.

00:03:52.080 --> 00:03:55.883
So it's going to be $25 million.

