Once again, pause the video,

00:04:07.950 --> 00:04:10.100
and see if you can work through that.

00:04:10.100 --> 00:04:12.750
So the tariff revenue
collected by the government,

00:04:12.750 --> 00:04:15.550
well, we went from a world
