00:06:56.520 --> 00:06:58.500
you've lost this entire triangle.

00:06:58.500 --> 00:07:01.660
Some of it is captured
by government revenue,

00:07:01.660 --> 00:07:04.720
but you also have deadweight loss.

00:07:04.720 --> 00:07:06.620
You also just have this section

00:07:06.620 --> 00:07:08.870
and this section as just deadweight loss.

00:07:08.870 --> 00:07:12.390
And so any tariff is going to reduce the,

00:07:12.390 --> 00:07:15.860
is going to reduce your
possible economic surplus.

00:07:15.860 --> 00:07:18.420
So a $0 tariff, theoretically,

00:07:18.420 --> 00:07:21.153
would maximize your
total economic surplus.

